@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000
@token = REEMPLAZAR_CON_JWT
@reservationId = REEMPLAZAR_CON_RESERVATION_ID

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Accept: application/json

### Usuario autenticado
GET {{baseUrl}}/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### Listar reservaciones del usuario autenticado
GET {{baseUrl}}/outlook/reservations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### Crear reservacion en Outlook
POST {{baseUrl}}/outlook/reservations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "title": "Reserva de aula 201",
  "description": "Clase de ingles intermedio",
  "start": "2026-04-05T09:00:00",
  "end": "2026-04-05T10:30:00",
  "location": "Edificio A, Aula 201",
  "timezone": "Central America Standard Time",
  "attendees": [
    "coordinacion@keyinstitute.edu.sv",
    "docente@keyinstitute.edu.sv"
  ]
}

### Cancelar reservacion en Outlook
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/outlook/reservations/{{reservationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "reason": "Se cancelo por cambio de horario"
}
